title: Garmin MapSource Cambodia v2.0 routable
description:
Rotweiler's All Cambodia Version v2.0 (2007) (GPS Maps Asia) gmapsupp.img version


Overview: Cambodia Routable Version 2. This routable map covers the
          entire Nation of Cambodia. Routing accuracy is navigation-ready.


It provides accurate detail for the Siem Reap area including the Angkor
Wat temples/ruin complexes, as well as complete, up-to-date, and
accurate streets routing for the capital, Phnom Penh. New build dated

November 12, 2007 includes new indexed POIs and roads for major cities.
Please note that this mapset is locked.

More Info: Updated: November 12, 2007 This map must be instaled first in
PC with Mapsource and then sent to device

This version only works with MapSource 6.13 by default, to make
it working with 6.14 you need to fix registry and .tdb file
with MapSource Maps Compatibility.exe.

Manufacturer's website: <a href="
http://www.gpsmapsasia.com/default.asp?Folder=2987" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
